## 5. Time and Space Complexity

| Method         | Time Complexity | Space Complexity |
|----------------|------------------|------------------|
| Built-in `max()` | O(n)             | O(1)             |
| Manual Loop     | O(n)             | O(1)             |

Where n is the number of elements.

